Excellent,
Since applying, ext3 x.16 to pre2 I have notice marked improvement in my
box'(s) stability, and responsiveness.  With the Pre4 and the new ext3
patch I have noticed even greater responsiveness, and Memory use has
definately dropped...a kernal untar was almost certain to eat almost the
entire 512MB on the box I am typing this from...that is no longer the
case.
